pageContext.claim: “I think my biggest fan in the whole world is Secretary General Stoltenberg, head of NATO. And he said he can't believe [members are spending more because of Trump], because for 20 years it went down. It's like a roller coaster dip. No -- none of this; just down. They paid less and less and less. And it got more expensive and more expensive with time.”
pageContext.analysis: False. NATO Secretary-General Stoltenberg made no such remark.
